Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.17,0:02:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去為迎擊大舉進攻的數億變動重力源
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.87,0:03:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾留下了在太陽系外圍使用黑洞兵器的記錄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.21,0:03:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是如今的「黑洞Exelion」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.52,0:03:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即「宇宙怪獸」的巢穴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.79,0:03:13.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推測在人類傾盡全力投入的反攻作戰之後
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.06,0:03:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由無人Buster Machine構成的\N太陽系絕對防衛系統被建造而成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.37,0:03:20.37,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,---------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.50,0:03:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時變動重力源的殘存勢力似乎倖存了下來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.47,0:03:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是人類已經沒有任何餘力了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.14,0:03:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才會選擇封印空間跳躍技術
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.04,0:03:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將自己封鎖於太陽系之中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.28,0:03:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防衛系統逐漸進化得更為強大、更有效率
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.42,0:03:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其最終獲得的形態
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.19,0:03:48.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻極為諷刺的 與敵人變動重力源非常相似
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.56,0:03:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現今被我們稱之為「宇宙怪獸」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.76,0:03:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防衛系統
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.78,0:03:59.06,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(420,370)\c&H000000&\bord0}第3軍司令官 德拉索提督
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.56,0:03:58.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是為了保護我們人類而建造的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.57,0:04:01.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾幾何時
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.14,0:04:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們似乎從自己應當保護的人類身上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.64,0:04:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感受到了與敵人變動重力源相同的威脅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.58,0:04:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.28,0:04:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Topless
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.19,0:04:16.20,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星之推動者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.22,0:04:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不清楚自治互助會的伙食究竟有多麼好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.69,0:04:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你也該習慣了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.20,0:04:31.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的同伴們也全都在軍方的管理下接受治療哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.73,0:04:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在設施內只要戴著矯正裝置 就不會造成多大的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.91,0:04:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論Topless這種病有多麼可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.42,0:04:50.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦事件之後
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.42,0:04:51.48,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(430,370)\fad(500,0)}太陽系 新10號行星
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.05,0:04:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於我們而言的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.09,0:04:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徹底改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.66,0:04:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面對真正的宇宙怪獸 變動重力源
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.13,0:05:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的力量根本不堪一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.10,0:05:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Topless已經不再是拯救人類的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.77,0:05:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Topless雖然是屬於青少年特有的前額葉異常現象
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.08,0:05:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只要早期治療 仍有希望重新融入社會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.08,0:05:20.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前已著手訂立藥物與外科治療的法令依據
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.62,0:05:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已於前天發佈毀棄條約事項
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.29,0:05:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並完成對自治互助會的強制徵收
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.09,0:05:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此一來 即可著手準備與「宇宙怪獸」進行和談
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.23,0:05:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的運氣不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.30,0:05:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎來了Buster Machine 7號
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.81,0:05:49.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然能到這裏來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.58,0:05:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼晚才來探訪 真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.35,0:05:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 真的很對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.39,0:06:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想說帶一些姐姐喜歡吃的東西來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.02,0:06:04.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一會是身體檢查 一會兒又是心理測驗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.66,0:06:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們一直不肯放我出來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.73,0:06:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種邊境 虧你能拿到這些
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.27,0:06:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我開口
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.67,0:06:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些特務大叔們就會想辦法幫我找來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.60,0:06:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚吃的還是北京烤鴨和鵝肝醬呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.91,0:06:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎就算想去地球也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.58,0:06:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們說好了 要去姐姐的家鄉找雲雀對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.78,0:06:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.05,0:06:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這只雲雀可以給我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.72,0:06:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是雲雀 是鶴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.89,0:06:36.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主的手藝很差啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.39,0:06:41.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在地球 送人這個就是希望對方能恢復健康
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.33,0:06:44.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實應該由探病的人來送才對
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.60,0:06:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐果然很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.53,0:07:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那頂安全帽很拉風嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.46,0:07:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.77,0:07:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看得很開呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.84,0:07:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前…覺得很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.04,0:07:25.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以在能力消失前就先提出喪失申請
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.71,0:07:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離開了dix-neuf
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.01,0:07:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒去確認能力是否消失 也就用不著絕望了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.81,0:07:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 都是以前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.58,0:07:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今我只是Buster Machine公社的承包維修工
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.47,0:07:52.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你用不著替它難過
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.74,0:07:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左手原本就是義肢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.71,0:08:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,插在那裏的那根角 年代更是久遠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.21,0:08:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據公社的記錄 那是500年前戰鬥時留下的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.08,0:08:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不將它修好？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,dix-neuf似乎不願意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.32,0:08:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擦過腦幹 整支貫穿著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.62,0:08:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也因為這樣造成幾個Exotic Maneuver無法使用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.82,0:08:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬一處理不好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.43,0:08:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可能會失去寶貴的戰鬥經驗值
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.13,0:08:25.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它代替了短暫的Topless 跨越時代累積經驗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.23,0:08:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是人工智能的存在目的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.44,0:08:30.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.41,0:08:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歷任駕駛員的塗鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.21,0:08:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這部分屬於六度修改之前的舊裝甲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.11,0:08:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是40任之前的前輩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.92,0:08:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「十六夜 靜默之夜獨自上路」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.12,0:08:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「他停在原地 我離開此處」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.96,0:08:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看得懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.06,0:08:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是哪個時代 大家都只能注定單戀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.53,0:08:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留下的只有戰鬥經驗值
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.93,0:08:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們則會被人遺忘
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.07,0:08:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼可拉呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.30,0:09:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說他一直持續發著低燒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.68,0:09:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰在那裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.75,0:09:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.32,0:09:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新來的大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.05,0:09:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我應該說過不可以隨便進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.92,0:09:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.19,0:09:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我會好好反省的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.36,0:09:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.36,0:09:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做…做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.86,0:09:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說還是想請你教她折
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.63,0:09:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就去一趟嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.90,0:09:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可是她的姐姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.91,0:09:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.61,0:09:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.45,0:09:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.59,0:09:56.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我害怕獨自啟程
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.73,0:09:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想要一份餞別禮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.76,0:10:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你願意送我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.56,0:10:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要得到你的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.43,0:10:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你本身就是Buster Machine吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.97,0:10:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你不就等於是永恆的Topless嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.79,0:10:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.06,0:10:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.73,0:10:33.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾諾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.20,0:10:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.51,0:10:46.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不是我？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.41,0:10:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你總是充滿自信又強悍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.78,0:10:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使明知你的溫柔全是裝出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.18,0:10:54.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也還是那麼喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.68,0:10:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算能力消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.12,0:10:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不願意看我一眼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.22,0:11:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我曾是Topless 所以才會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.89,0:11:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都幾歲的人了 什麼Buster Machine
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.56,0:11:06.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼和果子系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.23,0:11:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真像個傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.01,0:11:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.01,0:11:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准跟來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.61,0:11:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不是什麼姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.58,0:11:36.27,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(420,370)}旗艦 卡拉柯姆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.79,0:11:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是最初觀測到異狀時的影像
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.79,0:11:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊則是12分鐘前的影像
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.99,0:11:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為數驚人的「宇宙怪獸」開始集結
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.76,0:11:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「宇宙怪獸」的巢穴是人類從未涉足的神秘空域
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.84,0:11:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是吸積盤內部 無法進行X射線和重力波探測
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.84,0:11:53.33,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}【吸積盤】（Accretion Disk）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.84,0:11:53.33,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\pos(35,35)}吸積物質在緻密天體周圍形成的盤狀物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.41,0:11:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若想確認內部的狀況 只能派人直接進入
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.38,0:11:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由與泰坦事件的相似性來推測…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.55,0:12:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的變動重力源將會再度入侵太陽系嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.74,0:12:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們會回來吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.51,0:12:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.91,0:12:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩天後
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.08,0:12:36.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾諾與我加入了準備前往「宇宙怪獸」巢穴的艦隊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.59,0:12:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都對諾諾寄予厚望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.19,0:12:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認為Buster Machine7號會拯救人類
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.83,0:12:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 就不需要我了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.87,0:13:02.42,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽系 原13號行星 雷王星
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.47,0:13:06.52,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喪失9成的質量僅殘留中心核 現在已非行星
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.26,0:13:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不清楚原因
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.57,0:13:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火星的鳥全都滅絕了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.37,0:13:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道火星上最後一隻鳥的故事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.68,0:13:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從破殼而出的那刻起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.61,0:13:38.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就已經是最後一隻了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.95,0:13:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她從未曾飛上過天空
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.68,0:13:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一直站在水邊 從未嘗試飛翔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.46,0:13:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.76,0:13:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在長大後的某個日子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.43,0:13:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流星群劃過的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.66,0:13:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她飛起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.70,0:14:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彷彿是要追逐流星一般
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.60,0:14:04.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許是飛往星星的世界了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.44,0:14:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捨棄了土生土長的火星
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.82,0:14:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是她最後的記錄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.54,0:14:37.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於前方展開的「宇宙怪獸」 數量7萬5千
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.51,0:14:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍在持續增加中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.71,0:14:41.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8萬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.55,0:14:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}8萬5千
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.08,0:14:45.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們真的不會攻擊我們嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.78,0:14:48.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是守護巢穴的近衛部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.32,0:14:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}9萬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.67,0:14:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}9萬5千
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.82,0:14:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是來迎接7號的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.02,0:14:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超過10萬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.49,0:14:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7號
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.61,0:15:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.01,0:15:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,數量如此龐大的「宇宙怪獸」 惟7號一人之命是從
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.95,0:15:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這幅光景 就連身為Topless的你也會大為震驚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.45,0:15:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就是「宇宙怪獸」的女王
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.55,0:15:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶你隨行是7號的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.82,0:15:31.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是想展示你們之間力量的差異吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.10,0:15:58.97,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽系 新11號行星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.02,0:16:02.30,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑洞 Exelion
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.02,0:16:02.30,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(100,200)}＊前作中宇宙戰艦Exelion在雷王星軌道引爆其內部坍縮爐所形成的黑洞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.81,0:16:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「宇宙怪獸」集中的能層邊緣附近
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.81,0:16:24.57,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}【能層】（ergosphere）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.81,0:16:24.57,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\pos(35,35)}旋轉黑洞的視界與無限紅移面之間的區域
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.65,0:16:27.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現逆向的重力變動值
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.18,0:16:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其規模無法與泰坦事件相比擬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.55,0:16:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個就是變動重力源？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.99,0:16:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從黑洞裏爬了出來？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.92,0:16:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從這個變動重力源被Exelion困住以來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.40,0:16:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「宇宙怪獸」們一直持續致力將其封印住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.03,0:16:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了保護人類
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.94,0:16:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.47,0:16:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它正企圖打破黑洞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.68,0:16:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Buster Machine7號前往
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.60,0:17:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在用微型黑洞填補裂縫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.87,0:17:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改變周圍的物理空間 形成坍縮爐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.37,0:17:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是現今已經失傳了的技術
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.91,0:17:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那神一般的力量能拯救我們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.31,0:17:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「宇宙怪獸」的女王？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.75,0:17:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 她根本就是太陽系的女神
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.95,0:17:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7…號
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.39,0:17:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 下令艦隊前進
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.42,0:17:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用重力{Gravitron}炮進行掩護
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.53,0:17:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有我們這支宇宙最強艦隊與7號同進退
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.43,0:17:49.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何事物都不足為懼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.26,0:17:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非戰鬥員請離開艦橋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.93,0:17:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然會礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.17,0:17:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全員第一種戰鬥態勢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.94,0:17:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備炮擊進行重力消耗戰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.68,0:18:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,76 78 80…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.09,0:18:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦首重力炮 發射
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.10,0:18:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.07,0:18:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它將空間扭曲了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.07,0:18:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重力變動值異常上升
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.21,0:18:31.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可視波長圈即將浮上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.91,0:18:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.68,0:18:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要溢出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.50,0:19:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變動值的直徑超過1萬2千公里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.01,0:19:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1萬2千公里？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.68,0:19:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比地球還要大嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.78,0:19:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且尚未展露全體
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.35,0:19:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7號發出光束攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.26,0:19:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連7號的光束都無法…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.30,0:19:28.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.57,0:19:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提督 請下令全員離艦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.37,0:19:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也要盡速離開
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.61,0:19:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下令所有人員立刻離艦…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.08,0:19:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還可以容納一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.45,0:19:47.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動作快 這是最後一艘逃生艇了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.65,0:19:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.37,0:20:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼可拉也變成那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.11,0:20:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙胞胎還有大家都死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.82,0:20:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手…在發抖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.49,0:20:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.63,0:20:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從最早在火星上認識那時開始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.33,0:20:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「宇宙怪獸」就一直在找諾諾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.63,0:20:43.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們想要帶回自己的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.57,0:20:48.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾諾好強 我跟她差得可遠了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.18,0:20:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從一開始就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.92,0:21:06.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾諾一直很想變得跟姐姐一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.13,0:21:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都好羨慕姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.93,0:21:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.80,0:21:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐和諾諾莉莉非常像
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.67,0:21:22.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實諾諾莉莉並不特別
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.78,0:21:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她只是個普通的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.45,0:21:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在顫抖？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.33,0:21:43.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是世界改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.10,0:21:44.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是諾諾改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.77,0:21:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改變的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.94,0:21:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.91,0:21:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起飛吧 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.05,0:22:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,dix-neuf
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.50,0:22:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連同本艦共殘存12艘艦艇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.56,0:22:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旗艦識別信號消失…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.97,0:22:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「宇宙怪獸」完全不是對手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.67,0:22:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連7號也奈何不了它嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.42,0:22:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提督 讓艦隊退下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.45,0:22:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來對付它
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.69,0:22:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是剛才的Topless嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.89,0:22:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要投擲雷王星撞擊目標
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.69,0:22:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請退避到衝擊波範圍之外
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.13,0:22:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在胡說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.83,0:22:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類是不可能辦到那種事的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.87,0:22:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.27,0:22:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要和諾諾在一起 無論什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.44,0:22:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都辦得到！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.27,0:23:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exotic Maneuver
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.85,0:23:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Topless連星球都能推動嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.22,0:24:21.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以秒速20公里直接撞擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.62,0:24:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.20,0:24:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.40,0:24:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它並不是從Exelion黑洞裏出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.91,0:24:41.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是吞噬了整個Exelion
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.98,0:24:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠自由操縱黑洞
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.58,0:24:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使以雷王星撞擊也不會死的人類天敵
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.48,0:24:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觀測到以太分離波
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.19,0:24:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推測變動重力源企圖從本空域進行空間跳躍
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.59,0:24:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離到達空間跳躍臨界點還有300
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.13,0:25:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是現在無法解決它 人類會徹底滅亡的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.53,0:25:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將殘存艦艇集合起來
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.97,0:25:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少要給它一擊…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.84,0:25:11.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是白費力氣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.48,0:25:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 如果是7號的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.45,0:25:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾諾 你明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.69,0:25:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擊倒它的機會只有它在進行空間跳躍前的現在
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.59,0:25:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們需要比行星撞擊更加強大的能量
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.20,0:25:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓7號進入雷王星殘存的中心核
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.07,0:25:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以微型黑洞為導火線 誘發坍縮連鎖反應
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.87,0:25:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要讓雷王星成為黑洞嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.11,0:25:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種近距離的超重力崩潰
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.35,0:25:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該足以打倒變動重力源
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.55,0:26:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要讓她捨身作戰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.15,0:26:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 我不會讓諾諾一個人去
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.76,0:26:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.13,0:26:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正心跳不已
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.59,0:26:07.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們兩人將要拯救世界
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.56,0:26:11.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起化作星辰吧 諾諾
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.28,0:26:25.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？ 諾諾
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.92,0:26:31.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾諾
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.30,0:26:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾諾？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.53,0:26:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Buster Machine7號拒絕出戰逃走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.77,0:26:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然被她捨棄 就等於是喪失了防衛系統
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.05,0:27:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後我們只能靠自己的力量來對抗變動重力源了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.25,0:27:08.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 這樣也好
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.09,0:27:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是人類要真正長大…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.53,0:27:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所必須經過的儀式吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.00,0:27:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 沒想到她居然會臨陣脫逃
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.17,0:27:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離空間跳躍臨界 1.5 1.2
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.14,0:27:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提督 變動重力源即將進行空間跳躍
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.29,0:27:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾諾
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.63,0:27:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾諾！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.77,0:27:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾諾！
